snippet.title: Antiprism Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
We're very happy to announce Antiprism - the world's first twin-ship shoot'em'up exclusively for VR! 
Support us by wishlisting on Steam: http://bit.ly/antiprismsteam
Check out the announcement post here https://zerofun.games/blog/announcing-antiprism/  

Trailer music:
Dvořák - Symphony No. 9 (From the New World), 3rd movement
